title: Saudi Assistant Defense Minister calls on COAS
content:
RAWALPINDI, Jan 25 (APP):Assistant Minister of Defense, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia (KSA), Major General Talal Abdullah Al-Otaibi called on Chief of Army Staff (COAS), General Syed Asim Munir here at General Headquarters (GHQ), the Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR) news release on Wednesday said.
